Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.14,zhu,,0,0,0,,秋野早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,地獄少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:55.65,biaoti,,0,0,0,,看不見 聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原來真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你在猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你想放逐到地獄的真的是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不 肯定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,秋野對著我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他人也拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一起聊天的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,井本 遠藤 緒方 神谷…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,每人只能將一個人流放到地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別太貪心了 大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎 不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走了 菊理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一下再來吧 大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,靜香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 這麼晚了還大吼大叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛才說「救救我」了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都說沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要維護豐臣政權的石田三成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,與家康的衝突愈演愈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,肥屁的襪子是黃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,沾上了屁的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,吃番薯 噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,噗~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,噗~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:12.23,pm1,,0,0,0,,屁罐子啊w
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,又弄掉了
