Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,神谷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,被期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,神谷啊 我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,秋野怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,胖太拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,該怎麼做 胖太？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,是啊是啊 胖太大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,坐等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,急急急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:45.72,pm1,,0,0,0,,死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.72,pm4,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,482)}死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,湯川不可能做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,night 橫田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,請問橫田同學是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,橫田 有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,胖太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:53.58,pm1,,0,0,0,,肥屁真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:53.58,pm1,,0,0,0,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:53.58,pm1,,0,0,0,,別讓她進教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:53.58,pm1,,0,0,0,,讓她退學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:53.58,pm1,,0,0,0,,但是不知道她會對我們做什麼
